  "title": "Aircon Sales and Maintenance Executive",
  "description": "<p><u><em>Job details</em></u></p>\n<p>· $2500++ (Negotiable with commission)</p>\n<p>· 5 days, 9.00am to 6.00pm</p>\n<p>· Location: Bedok North</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><u><em>Roles &amp; Responsibilities</em></u></p>\n<p>- To sell aircon related soft services, hard services, consulting and projects</p>\n<p>- To understand the current Aircon Management market, and the future Aircon Management model</p>\n<p>- To understand and propose a viable pricing model to ensure profitability and win-win</p>\n<p>- To formulate short term, mid term and long term strategy, drive sales activities and acquisition of new business</p>\n<p>- To develop sales master plan</p>\n<p>- To find potential new customers and convert them into customers</p>\n<p>- To conduct cold calls and face to face meeting with customers</p>\n<p>- Customer relationship management to ensure customers’ satisfaction</p>\n<p>- To develop presentation deck, technical evaluation on request for quotation, participate in technical and bid clarification, and the development of quotation, scope and deliverables proposal to customers</p>\n<p>- To create, negotiate and close commercial and technical terms and conditions sales agreement</p>\n<p>- To ensure profitable sales closure, drives peak performance and sales success across cross functional team</p>\n<p>- To ensure products / services and solutions deliver meets the customers satisfactions</p>\n<p>- To fulfil the roles and duties of a sales account executive</p>\n<p>- To meet the agreed upon sales target set and agreed together with the management</p>\n<p>- To manage clients and build relationships to ensure that they are satisfied and positive from the services and solution provided</p>\n<p>- To provide innovative solution to drive customer satisfaction and profitability</p>\n<p>- To partner with other team members to deliver value to customer</p>\n<p>- To also work on growing and developing existing clients, together with generating new business.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><u><em>Job Requirements</em></u></p>\n<p>· Have a good level of MS office Word, and Excel skills.</p>\n<p>· Preferably candidates who are able to start work on short notice.</p>\n<p>· With/without working experiences are welcome to apply.</p>",
